To build SqueezeLite for Android the following depencies are required:

  - Android SDK (sdk platform 34, build tools 34.0.0)
  - Android NDK r27
  - Meson 0.56.0
  - Ninja
  - Cmake
  - pkg-config
  - libtool
  - python 3.9+

Build steps:
  - mkdir build
  - cd build
  - ../build.sh
  - cd ..
  - ./gradlew assemble
